**Benefits**

• Centralized visibility for unresolved Cohesity backup failures
• Automated ServiceNow incident creation and 4-hour updates
• Reduced manual validation, consolidation, and reporting effort
• Avoids duplicate incident handling for the same failure cycle
• Tracks only active failures after later-success validation
• Reduces detection gaps using email alerts and PowerShell validation
• Improves operational follow-up with consistent failure reporting
